{"about_the_game":"GAMEPLAY<br />\r\nPlay as the fast and agile gunman, with a wide array of guns, environmental and indirect ways of fight, and powerful kicks.<br />\r\nFace off against disturbing creatures, and bandits, dodge traps, and solve puzzles.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPLOT<br />\r\nHired to save a priest from a ruthless and sadistic vampire, a lone bounty hunter sets out on a journey to a cursed land, haunted by terrible creatures of the night.<br />\r\nThe lone gunslinger quickly discovers the horrible truth that people there are treated as livestock, preyed upon by supernatural evil. The worst among these monsters is an imprisoned vampire, who commands his vermin to hunt down unsuspecting villagers so that he may feast upon their blood.<br />\r\nThis arduous task will send the young gunslinger into an unforgiving fight for survival, making him question if hope can be found in such a place and if his strict morality can survive in such desperate times.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWEAPONS<br />\r\nUse a variety of guns, swords, and the environment to survive the unholy slaughter coming your way, from flintlock pistols, Mauser c96s, Winchesters, shotguns, and more.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228790/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1726778345","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228790/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1726778345","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228790/d72f4741061bcf5f72ba692960cbd4d9d563286c/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1726778345","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3228790/d72f4741061bcf5f72ba692960cbd4d9d563286c/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1726778345","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"GAMEPLAY<br />\r\nPlay as the fast and agile gunman, with a wide array of guns, environmental and indirec